        <abstract>
            <p>Returns [Andrew] Murray’s paper;</p>
            <p>especially values HD’s note that the same species of lice infect the different varieties of fowl, pigeon, and dog. Further queries about the relationship of the same species of pediculi to different domestic varieties.</p>
